1767431017788028821.Text: Sellus Gravius of Seyda Neen has tasked me with leading a band of adventurers out to the overrun fort of Firemoth. It is there that we will fight the skeleton army of Grurn and return with the Ward of Akavir.

735331089409329325.Text: I have returned the Ward of Akavir to Sellus Gravius in exchange for 3000 gold.
